<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 20:06:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴基斯坦西南部局势动荡，枪手杀害 6 名建筑工人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/gunmen-kill-6-construction-workers-in-volatile-southwestern-pakistan/articleshow/104430212.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104430212.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦警方周六表示，武装分子夜间在动荡的西南部俾路支省枪杀了六名建筑工人。警官希达亚图拉·达什提 (Hidayatullah Dashti) 表示，武装分子连夜向图尔巴特市 (Turbat) 的 8 名建筑工人开枪，该市位于该省首府奎达 (Quetta) 以南约 377 英里（约 606 公里）处。他说，其中两人幸存，并被送往医院接受治疗。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 18:51:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/gunmen-kill-6-construction-workers-in-volatile-southwestern-pakistan/articleshow/104430212.cms</guid></item><item><title>教师遇害后法国部署7000名士兵加强安保</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/france-deploys-7000-troops-for-extra-security-after-teacher-slain/articleshow/104430096.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104430096.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国总统马克龙部署了 7,000 名士兵加强安全巡逻，以应对炸弹警报和伊斯兰袭击。卢浮宫博物馆、凡尔赛宫和巴黎里昂火车站因误报而被疏散。内政部长杰拉尔德·达尔马宁提到中东事件后出现了“圣战气氛”。马克龙办公室宣布，作为持续安全行动的一部分，将部署这些士兵，直至另行通知。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 18:35:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/france-deploys-7000-troops-for-extra-security-after-teacher-slain/articleshow/104430096.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列外交部：哈马斯不让人们离开城市，将其用作盾牌</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-not-letting-people-leave-cities-using-them-as-shield-israel-foreign-ministry/articleshow/104429997.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429997.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列外交部发言人利奥尔·海亚特周六表示，哈马斯利用加沙平民作为保护自己的盾牌，并从人口稠密地区瞄准以色列。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 18:13:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-not-letting-people-leave-cities-using-them-as-shield-israel-foreign-ministry/articleshow/104429997.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人在为加沙攻势做准备时受到“灾难”的困扰</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-haunted-by-nakba-while-bracing-for-gaza-offensive/articleshow/104429922.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429922.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙居民面临以色列的轰炸和物资短缺，尽管下达了疏散令，他们仍拒绝离开家园。流离失所的想法与 1948 年以色列建国期间的战争相呼应，这场战争被称为“Nakba”或“灾难”，当时许多巴勒斯坦人被迫离开家园。巴勒斯坦难民的命运是巴以和平进程中一个有争议的问题。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 18:08:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-haunted-by-nakba-while-bracing-for-gaza-offensive/articleshow/104429922.cms</guid></item><item><title>加拿大确认以色列第四例死亡，寻求加沙和约旦河西岸撤离</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canada-confirms-fourth-death-in-israel-seeks-gaza-west-bank-evacuations/articleshow/104430089.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104430089.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加拿大外交部长梅兰妮·乔利确认，哈马斯最近对以色列发动袭击，造成第四名加拿大人死亡。她正在努力从加沙和西岸撤离公民。失踪的 22 岁加拿大人 Shir Georgy 的家人证实了她的死亡。乔利正在努力让加拿大人通过拉法边境口岸离开加沙进入埃及，并乘坐巴士离开西岸进入约旦。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 18:41:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canada-confirms-fourth-death-in-israel-seeks-gaza-west-bank-evacuations/articleshow/104430089.cms</guid></item><item><title>“他们为了好玩而杀人”：失去女儿的美国妇女敦促美国人不要支持哈马斯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/they-kill-for-fun-us-woman-who-lost-her-daughter-urges-americans-not-to-support-hamas/articleshow/104429812.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429812.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名出生在美国的妇女的女儿在以色列音乐节上的哈马斯恐怖袭击中丧生，她敦促美国人重新考虑对该组织的支持。这次袭击造成 260 人死亡，这名妇女称这是一次纳粹组织的行动。当言论自由允许支持恐怖分子时，她对言论自由的想法提出质疑。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 18:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/they-kill-for-fun-us-woman-who-lost-her-daughter-urges-americans-not-to-support-hamas/articleshow/104429812.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国首相里希·苏纳克：“英国将永远与盟友站在一起反恐”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-will-always-stand-with-its-allies-against-terror-pm-rishi-sunak/articleshow/104429806.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429806.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;苏纳克在“X”上写道：“英国将始终与我们的盟友站在一起打击恐怖主义。在哈马斯对以色列无辜受害者发动恐怖袭击后，我部署了我们世界一流的军队来支持地区稳定，防止局势进一步升级并援助人道主义努力。”周六。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 17:53:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-will-always-stand-with-its-allies-against-terror-pm-rishi-sunak/articleshow/104429806.cms</guid></item><item><title>波兰准备举行高风险全国选举，情绪高涨</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/emotions-run-high-as-poland-prepares-to-hold-a-high-stakes-national-election/articleshow/104429993.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429993.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波兰正在举行一场至关重要的选举，这将决定其民主、LGBTQ+ 权利和堕胎法的未来。执政的法律与正义党被指控削弱制衡并控制国家机构。支持者担心，如果该党失败，反对党将推行更加自由的政策。最近的民意调查显示，法律和正义党获得最多支持，但还不足以获得多数支持。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 18:16:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/emotions-run-high-as-poland-prepares-to-hold-a-high-stakes-national-election/articleshow/104429993.cms</guid></item><item><title>正在美国申请临时合法身份的委内瑞拉移民表示，这提供了一些缓解</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/venezuelan-migrants-who-are-applying-for-temporary-legal-status-in-the-us-say-it-offers-some-relief/articleshow/104429741.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429741.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登政府正在为居住在美国的委内瑞拉人提供临时合法身份，使他们更容易工作并避免被驱逐出境的恐惧。委内瑞拉人必须在 7 月 31 日之前抵达美国才有资格获得临时保护身份 (TPS)。政府还宣布重启飞往委内瑞拉的航班，驱逐未经授权的人。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 17:41:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/venezuelan-migrants-who-are-applying-for-temporary-legal-status-in-the-us-say-it-offers-some-relief/articleshow/104429741.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方发言人称以色列将很快袭击加沙城</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-military-spokesman-says-israel-to-strike-gaza-city-very-soon-/articleshow/104429636.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429636.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列军方发言人丹尼尔·哈加里少将宣布即将对加沙城发动袭击，并敦促居民搬迁到加沙地带南部，理由是哈马斯据称利用平民作为盾牌，而以色列正准备在持续冲突中发动潜在的地面进攻。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 17:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-military-spokesman-says-israel-to-strike-gaza-city-very-soon-/articleshow/104429636.cms</guid></item><item><title>在最近的罢工后，凯撒医疗机构与医护人员工会达成临时协议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/kaiser-permanente-reaches-a-tentative-deal-with-health-care-worker-unions-after-a-recent-strike/articleshow/104429558.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429558.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在针对工资和人员配置水平举行罢工后，代表 85,000 名医护人员的工会与 Kaiser Permanente 达成了临时协议。该协议包括加州最低时薪为 25 美元，其他州为 23 美元，并且四年内工资上涨 21%。该协议还解决了分包和外包问题，对现有劳动力进行投资，旨在解决人员危机。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 17:19:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/kaiser-permanente-reaches-a-tentative-deal-with-health-care-worker-unions-after-a-recent-strike/articleshow/104429558.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列警告真主党不要卷入加沙战争</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-warns-hezbollah-to-stay-out-of-gaza-war/articleshow/104429137.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429137.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列国家安全顾问查奇·哈内格比表示，与黎巴嫩真主党的敌对行动目前受到克制，以色列正在努力避免两线战争。哈内比警告真主党不要采取可能导致黎巴嫩毁灭的行动。他还承认，以色列情报部门在最近的袭击发生前评估哈马斯的意图时犯了一个错误。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 16:43:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-warns-hezbollah-to-stay-out-of-gaza-war/articleshow/104429137.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙的巴勒斯坦人努力遵守以色列的撤离命令，并面临严重的水资源短缺</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-in-gaza-struggle-to-follow-israeli-evacuation-order-and-face-dire-water-shortage/articleshow/104429200.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429200.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 16:48:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-in-gaza-struggle-to-follow-israeli-evacuation-order-and-face-dire-water-shortage/articleshow/104429200.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰财政部长表示，随着战争的拖延，捐助者越来越“疲倦”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-finance-minister-says-donor-tiredness-growing-as-war-drags-on/articleshow/104429122.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429122.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰财政部长谢尔盖·马尔琴科对获得财政支持表示担忧，因为捐助国正在将注意力转向即将举行的选举和地缘政治紧张局势。马尔琴科强调了与俄罗斯正在进行的战争，以及需要西方支持来弥补 2024 年 430 亿美元的预算缺口。不过，他指出，由于地缘政治变化和不同国家的内部政治背景，各国政府支持乌克兰的意愿有所下降。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 16:42:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-finance-minister-says-donor-tiredness-growing-as-war-drags-on/articleshow/104429122.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列总理在加沙边境访问时告诉部队“更多即将到来”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/more-is-coming-israel-pm-tells-troops-on-gaza-border-visit/articleshow/104429118.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429118.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;根据总理办公室发布的视频，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理周六对加沙边境附近的部队表示，以色列将“采取更多行动”回应哈马斯上周的震惊袭击。更多即将到来，”总理办公室称周六早些时候拍摄的视频中，可以听到穿着防弹衣的内塔尼亚胡对几名士兵说。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 16:41:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/more-is-coming-israel-pm-tells-troops-on-gaza-border-visit/articleshow/104429118.cms</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩市长：两名平民在以色列炮击中丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/two-civilians-killed-in-israel-shelling-of-lebanon-mayor/articleshow/104429017.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104429017.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 16:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/two-civilians-killed-in-israel-shelling-of-lebanon-mayor/articleshow/104429017.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国援助负责人：加沙局势“迅速变得难以为继”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-aid-chief-situation-is-gaza-fast-becoming-untenable/articleshow/104428904.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104428904.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国援助负责人警告说，加沙的人道主义局势正在变得不可持续。电力、水、燃料和食品供应严重短缺。这位援助负责人呼吁所有有影响力的国家确保尊重战争规则并防止局势进一步升级。他批评哈马斯武装分子和以色列的行动和言论。援助负责人对平民的苦难表示担忧，并呼吁释放人质。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 16:18:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-aid-chief-situation-is-gaza-fast-becoming-untenable/articleshow/104428904.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦正处于贫困的临界点：世界银行</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-at-tipping-point-on-poverty-world-bank/articleshow/104428953.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104428953.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;世界银行警告称，巴基斯坦正处于贫困危机边缘，40%的人口生活在贫困线以下。该银行的政策说明旨在为新政府提供指导，强调了去年有超过 1,250 万巴基斯坦人陷入贫困的事实。近年来，贫困率从34.2%上升至39.4%，更多人陷入贫困线以下。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 16:23:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-at-tipping-point-on-poverty-world-bank/articleshow/104428953.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我们都准备好了”：以色列总理内塔尼亚胡对加沙攻势</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/we-are-all-ready-israel-pm-netanyahu-on-gaza-offensive/articleshow/104428562.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104428562.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡表示，加沙地带的武装分子已做好准备，应对任何情况。他访问了加沙边境附近两个受灾最严重的社区，亲眼目睹了最近哈马斯袭击的后果。在埃及、以色列、美国和卡塔尔的参与下，加沙的外国人可以通过拉法过境点进入埃及。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 15:41:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/we-are-all-ready-israel-pm-netanyahu-on-gaza-offensive/articleshow/104428562.cms</guid></item><item><title>莫迪总理表示，印度将不遗余力举办 2036 年奥运会</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/india-will-leave-no-stone-unturned-in-hosting-2036-olympics-says-pm-modi/articleshow/104428681.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104428681.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;莫迪总理在国际奥委会第141届会议上表达了印度主办2036年奥运会的强烈愿望。他还提到印度有兴趣主办 2029 年青奥会。莫迪强调了体育在印度文化中的重要性，并表示印度将不遗余力地举办奥运会。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 15:53:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/india-will-leave-no-stone-unturned-in-hosting-2036-olympics-says-pm-modi/articleshow/104428681.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>